    caption: [Examples of chemicals that are proven or suspected neurotransmitters, organized by category. Includes acetylcholine, monoamines (catecholamines and indolamines), amino acids (excitatory and inhibitory), polypeptides, endocannabinoids, purines, and gases. Lists specific neurotransmitters within each category with their chemical classifications.],
    path: "../fig/image_place_holder.png"
